(Barbara) Yeah.

00:38:10,605 --> 00:38:12,173
How many of them, how to
get ahold of all of them.

00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:14,442
I'm gonna leave it up to them
at that point,

00:38:14,509 --> 00:38:15,443
and that is challenging.

