Daymond,
I know that market.

00:38:18,980 --> 00:38:20,648
I can get this into
all the motorcycle shops

00:38:20,715 --> 00:38:22,116
across North America
very easily,

00:38:22,183 --> 00:38:23,818
but I don't know
the fashion side.

00:38:23,885 --> 00:38:25,453
I can do the manufacturing.

00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:27,555
But I'm not doing
this deal without you.

00:38:27,622 --> 00:38:29,724
All right.

00:38:32,927 --> 00:38:35,096
You guys would be crazy
to deal with 'em.

00:38:36,698 --> 00:38:40,068
♪♪

00:38:46,107 --> 00:38:48,409
All right, ladies, ladies,
before you start,

00:38:48,476 --> 00:38:51,112
catastrophic move

00:38:51,179 --> 00:38:53,314
in trying
to convince the sharks

00:38:53,381 --> 00:38:55,316
that you are worth $2 million.

00:38:55,383 --> 00:38:56,517
And you admit it.

00:38:56,584 --> 00:38:59,053
However, we have let you
go back and reconsider.

00:38:59,120 --> 00:39:01,222
