50% equity.

00:39:09,597 --> 00:39:11,432
While you were out there,

00:39:11,499 --> 00:39:13,735
Robert and I
had a conversation.

00:39:13,801 --> 00:39:16,270
And Robert brings
something to the table

00:39:16,337 --> 00:39:18,806
because he has
a very good relationship

00:39:18,873 --> 00:39:22,010
with a lot
of motorcycle shops.

00:39:22,076 --> 00:39:24,312
So we want
to counteroffer you.

00:39:24,379 --> 00:39:26,114
